msg: Eliminate duplicate repository creation code from FSFS hotcopy.
Factor out most of svn_fs_fs__create into a svn_fs_fs__create_file_tree
function that creates all of the required files and sub-folders.  Use it
in hotcopy to create the empty target repository.
(svn_fs_fs__create_file_tree): Implement it with code taken from ...
(svn_fs_fs__create): ... this.  Keep only the parameter checking and
(hotcopy_create_empty_dest): Use the new private API to create the
target repo and tweak it to our needs.
